<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/21(Sat.)Fake-meat and fries: The rise of vegan fast food/'Dangerous' AI offers to write fake news(Host:Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=318&amp;p=334#p334"><![CDATA[
9/21(Sat.)Fake-meat and fries: The rise of vegan fast food/'Dangerous' AI offers to write fake news(Host:Danny)<br /><br />Article1:Fake-meat and fries: The rise of vegan fast food<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/av/uk-49551115/fake-meat-and-fries-the-rise-of-vegan-fast-food">https://www.bbc.com/news/av/uk-49551115 ... -fast-food</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion :<br />1. Are you a vegetarian? What do you think of vegetarian diet?<br />2. Have you been to a vegetarian restaurant? Is the vegetarian food in the film the same as you think?<br />3. These restaurants allow different people to eat together. In terms of diet, do you have any hobbies? Must have white rice, or must have meat... and so on?<br /><br /><br />Article2:'Dangerous' AI offers to write fake news<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-49446729">https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-49446729</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion :<br />1. How fake news influence people? What do you think about that?<br />2. Do you have any tips to judge fake news? Where did you get fake news?<br />3. If your friends or relatives tell you fake information, would you correct he/she?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<br /><br />Royal 三峽 , Royal new branch information,<br />Every Monday evening: 8:00pm- 10pm: 摩斯漢堡 北大特區 土城區學成路712號, next to the park.<br />Please keep contact with President Ophelia.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Sep 18, 2019 1:22 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
